race.comment: SPICY SEDUCTION (2) had the drop on the lead from the inside before drawing clear to score (25.52) at this track in a Grade 5 over 450m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Expected to be right there at the finish again. FRANKLIN AVENUE (7) jumped from the same box last time when a 5.5 lengths second (25.89) at this track over 450m. Leading player again. GLOWING ETHICS (6) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when second (28.44) at Bendigo. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Leading player again. NOT FORGIVEN (1) is worth consideration.
